label: thymine (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in both polarity. HILz: pk at rt +0.25 is in source frag of thymidine

label: uracil (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in polarity. HILz: pks at rt +0.4 and +1 min are in src frags of deoxyuridine and uridine

label: adenine (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in both polarity. HILz: pks at rt -0.4 and +0.23 = in src frags of deoxyadenosine and adenosine

label: xanthine (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in both polarity. HILz: pk at RT +7.5 min is in src frag of xanthosine

label: ribose (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in neg polarity. HILz: pk at RT +8 min = second isotope of methionine

label: hypoxanthine (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in both polarity. HILz: pk in pos mode at rt +1.8 min = in src frag of inosine

label: cytosine (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in both polarity. HILz: pks at rt +0.55 and 1.55 are in src frags of deoxycytidine and cytidine

label: phenylacetic acid (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in polarity. HILz: pk at RT +1.5 min = second isotope of adenine

label: phenylalanine (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in both polarity. HILz: pos mode is very noisy

label: urocanic acid (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in both polarity. hilZ: smaller pk at ~2 min,

label: pipecolic acid (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in both polarity. HILz: pk at rt +6 min is in src frag of lysine (+)

label: 5-oxo-proline (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in polarity. HILz: pks at rt +1.9, +2.99, +3.79, +4.69 = in src frags of hydroxyproline (-), Gln (-), N-acetyl-Glu, Glu

label: sucrose (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in both polarity. HILz: multiple peaks

label: asparagine (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in pos polarity. HILz: pks in neg mode at RT - 2.15 and -0.15 are in src frags of citrulline and arginine

label: gamma-Aminobutyric acid (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in both polarity. HILz: pk at rt -0.5 min is in src frag of 4-guanidinobutanoic acid

label: lysine (unlabeled)
indentification notes: ionizes in both polarity. HILz: neg pk at rt -1.9 min = in src frac of N-acetyl-Lys
